"AssemblyInfo.cs" Assembly Information for CSScript plugin
"CsScript.cs" C# Source Code for CSScript
"CsScript.csproj" Project File for CSScript plugin
"CsScript.sln" Solution File for CSScript plugin
"DotNetPluginSDK.cs" .NET Plugin SDK for TCC
"template.csx" A template C# file, for testing CSScript plugin
"test_template.btm" A .btm that runs the template.csx file using CSScript
